WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
A young seal rests on the wet sand by the sea.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
Its spotted body slowly slides, leaving a trail behind.

00:06.000 --> 00:08.000
The sound of the waves accompanies its calm movement.

00:08.000 --> 00:10.000
It looks toward the horizon, curious, before continuing its way to the water.

